47
00:03:19,844 --> 00:03:22,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I can't tell, because I lost to that Lan-Evo</b></font>

48
00:03:22,844 --> 00:03:26,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>before I saw his full capabilities.</b></font>

49
00:03:29,784 --> 00:03:33,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm getting upset just talking to you about it.</b></font>

50
