113
00:07:50,274 --> 00:07:55,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Have I not yet overcome</i>
<i>my complex about Ryosuke?</i></b></font>

114
00:07:55,914 --> 00:07:59,184
