139
00:09:37,554 --> 00:09:41,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Incredible! The FC is cornering
while blocking the Evo III!</b></font>

140
00:09:41,224 --> 00:09:43,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Go, Ryosuke Takahashi!</b></font>

141
00:09:43,754 --> 00:09:46,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Go! Go! Go!</b></font>

142
