151
00:10:53,464 --> 00:10:57,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I can't believe Kyoichi couldn't beat him.</b></font>

152
00:10:57,804 --> 00:10:59,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>An amazing course record.</b></font>

153
00:10:59,804 --> 00:11:03,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I've never seen Ryosuke go that fast.</b></font>

154
00:11:03,574 --> 00:11:06,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Why is he faster in battles than usual?</b></font>

155
00:11:06,504 --> 00:11:10,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>My brother usually leaves
enough of a safety margin</b></font>

156
00:11:10,014 --> 00:11:14,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>to avoid crashing during our time trials.</b></font>

157
00:11:14,184 --> 00:11:16,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>When he's forced to raise the bar,</b></font>

158
00:11:16,684 --> 00:11:19,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>a record like this is the natural result.</b></font>

159
00:11:19,854 --> 00:11:23,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That Evo III was a tough opponent.</b></font>

160
00:11:23,124 --> 00:11:25,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>So he got a bit serious.</b></font>

161
00:11:25,524 --> 00:11:27,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Wow!</b></font>

162
00:11:31,064 --> 00:11:32,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What a win!</b></font>

163
00:11:32,404 --> 00:11:35,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That corner was amazing!</b></font>

164
00:11:38,074 --> 00:11:42,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I want to ask you something, Ryosuke.</b></font>

165
00:11:42,744 --> 00:11:45,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What's the difference between us?</b></font>

166
00:11:45,744 --> 00:11:48,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Why can't I beat you?</b></font>

167
00:11:48,584 --> 00:11:50,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I just don't get it.</b></font>

168
00:11:50,584 --> 00:11:53,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Please tell me.</b></font>

169
00:11:53,054 --> 00:11:57,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>In my opinion, your technique
is almost as good as mine.</b></font>

170
00:11:57,894 --> 00:12:01,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No need for consolation. Just tell me why!</b></font>

171
00:12:01,264 --> 00:12:06,604
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm saying that it's not
because of your technique.</b></font>

172
00:12:06,604 --> 00:12:09,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Your weakness is your right turn.</b></font>

173
00:12:09,334 --> 00:12:11,604
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Not all right turns...</b></font>

174
00:12:11,604 --> 00:12:13,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...but at certain right turns,</b></font>

175
00:12:13,944 --> 00:12:16,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>your weakness surfaces.</b></font>

176
00:12:16,614 --> 00:12:18,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Right turns?</b></font>

177
00:12:18,114 --> 00:12:21,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>To the right of the center line is a "dead zone"</b></font>

178
00:12:21,614 --> 00:12:24,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>occupied by opposing traffic.</b></font>

179
00:12:24,124 --> 00:12:26,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You can't attack a right-hand corner</b></font>

180
00:12:26,624 --> 00:12:29,294
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>without worrying about a head-on collision.</b></font>

181
00:12:29,294 --> 00:12:32,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No one can give it 100%.</b></font>

182
00:12:32,124 --> 00:12:34,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But with experience and effort,</b></font>

183
00:12:34,634 --> 00:12:37,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>you can come close to 100%.</b></font>

184
00:12:39,134 --> 00:12:42,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Do you understand, Kyoichi?
That's the difference.</b></font>

185
00:12:42,734 --> 00:12:47,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>In motorsports, you don't have
to worry about opposing traffic.</b></font>

186
00:12:47,044 --> 00:12:50,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The Gymkhana circuit
doesn't have two-way traffic.</b></font>

187
00:12:50,314 --> 00:12:56,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>And your home course,
Nikko Irohazaka, is one-way,</b></font>

188
00:12:56,284 --> 00:12:58,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>so there's no opposing traffic.</b></font>

189
00:12:59,924 --> 00:13:01,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>In your counterattack,</b></font>

190
00:13:01,924 --> 00:13:05,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>you always stay outside at right-hand corners.</b></font>

191
00:13:05,724 --> 00:13:08,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I read that as meaning
you're afraid of the inside.</b></font>

192
00:13:08,864 --> 00:13:13,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>In the race against the Eight-Six,
you showed me too much,</b></font>

193
00:13:13,064 --> 00:13:15,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>which is why you lost.</b></font>

194
00:13:27,084 --> 00:13:29,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>You beat me, Ryosuke.</i></b></font>

195
00:13:29,214 --> 00:13:33,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>My belief that I had caught up</i>
<i>with you was an illusion.</i></b></font>

196
00:13:35,094 --> 00:13:38,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>You have street "charisma."</i></b></font>

197
00:13:39,894 --> 00:13:42,134
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It was amazing!</b></font>

198
00:13:42,134 --> 00:13:46,604
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I realized again how great
Ryosuke Takahashi really is.</b></font>

199
00:13:46,604 --> 00:13:50,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Anyway, the Lan-Evo squad
"storm" that threatened Gunma</b></font>

200
00:13:50,634 --> 00:13:52,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>has blown itself out,</b></font>

201
00:13:52,944 --> 00:13:55,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and peace has been restored.</b></font>

202
00:13:55,144 --> 00:13:58,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah. I should've gone to watch the race.</b></font>

203
00:13:58,144 --> 00:14:02,084
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>By the way, were Takumi and Itsuki with you?</b></font>

204
00:14:02,084 --> 00:14:04,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I didn't see them there.</b></font>

205
00:14:04,424 --> 00:14:06,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Maybe Takumi didn't feel like it</b></font>

206
00:14:06,884 --> 00:14:09,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>after his loss the other night.</b></font>

207
00:14:09,394 --> 00:14:11,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm sure he didn't.</b></font>

208
00:14:11,064 --> 00:14:14,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Even we are still in shock.</b></font>

209
00:14:14,094 --> 00:14:17,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He specifically told me
he wouldn't go to Akagi.</b></font>

210
00:14:17,564 --> 00:14:21,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I wonder what changed his mind.</b></font>

211
00:14:25,944 --> 00:14:29,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm so happy that Ryosuke Takahashi won!</b></font>

212
00:14:29,674 --> 00:14:34,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Now it's official that
Gunma's standard is very high.</b></font>

213
00:14:36,214 --> 00:14:38,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll see you in class!</b></font>

214
00:14:44,924 --> 00:14:49,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey! You won't believe this,
Takumi. The other day...</b></font>

215
00:14:50,904 --> 00:14:53,134
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Wait, Takumi!</b></font>

216
00:14:55,104 --> 00:14:58,934
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm sorry, but I don't feel like talking to you.</b></font>

217
00:15:07,344 --> 00:15:10,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"A few days later"</b></font>

218
00:15:10,714 --> 00:15:14,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What? My dad's Eight-Six?</b></font>

219
00:15:14,354 --> 00:15:16,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It must be a mistake.</b></font>

220
00:15:16,854 --> 00:15:18,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't know anything about it.</b></font>

221
00:15:18,564 --> 00:15:23,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>One of our team members says
he saw it in Akina one night.</b></font>

222
00:15:23,234 --> 00:15:27,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It was a three-door "panda" Trueno.</b></font>

223
00:15:27,004 --> 00:15:29,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't think it was ours.</b></font>

224
00:15:29,874 --> 00:15:32,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Where is your dad's car, anyway?</b></font>

225
00:15:32,704 --> 00:15:35,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't really know.</b></font>

226
00:15:35,374 --> 00:15:37,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We towed it from Akagi,</b></font>

227
00:15:37,544 --> 00:15:40,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and my dad took it somewhere after that.</b></font>

228
00:15:40,844 --> 00:15:43,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What about your morning deliveries?</b></font>

229
00:15:43,554 --> 00:15:47,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm using a pickup truck my dad brought in.</b></font>

230
00:15:47,124 --> 00:15:49,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Don't tell me that your legendary Eight-Six</b></font>

231
00:15:49,894 --> 00:15:53,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>is at a scrap yard right now.</b></font>

232
00:15:53,394 --> 00:15:55,134
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll cry!</b></font>

233
00:15:55,134 --> 00:15:57,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I doubt it.</b></font>

234
00:15:57,634 --> 00:16:00,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>My dad said he would put in another engine.</b></font>

235
00:16:00,634 --> 00:16:03,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Seriously? What kind of engine?</b></font>

236
00:16:03,874 --> 00:16:08,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I doubt it'll be another normal 4AG engine.</b></font>

237
00:16:08,714 --> 00:16:11,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Maybe it'll be a turbo!</b></font>

238
00:16:11,814 --> 00:16:16,084
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I have no interest in that, really.</b></font>

239
00:16:17,154 --> 00:16:18,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Why is that?</b></font>

240
00:16:18,424 --> 00:16:20,254
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I think that, of all parts,</b></font>

241
00:16:20,254 --> 00:16:24,824
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>the engine is the most
important element of a car.</b></font>

242
00:16:24,824 --> 00:16:29,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--I guess so.
--It's like the brain in a human body.</b></font>

243
00:16:30,834 --> 00:16:32,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey, Takumi...</b></font>

244
00:16:32,004 --> 00:16:35,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>People usually compare it to the human heart.</b></font>

245
00:16:35,504 --> 00:16:37,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Is that right?</b></font>

246
00:16:37,004 --> 00:16:39,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's the heart, then.</b></font>

247
00:16:39,504 --> 00:16:43,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'd just hate to have another engine in it.</b></font>

248
00:16:43,514 --> 00:16:47,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It would feel like a different car.</b></font>

249
00:16:47,384 --> 00:16:49,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I guess I can see that.</b></font>

250
00:16:49,554 --> 00:16:51,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're attached to it.</b></font>

251
00:16:51,884 --> 00:16:54,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I can understand how you feel...</b></font>

252
00:16:54,924 --> 00:16:56,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...but we can't help wondering</b></font>

253
00:16:56,924 --> 00:17:00,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>what kind of engine it'll have.</b></font>

254
00:17:22,154 --> 00:17:24,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>How does it feel, Bunta?</b></font>

255
00:17:24,054 --> 00:17:26,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's getting better,</b></font>

256
00:17:26,384 --> 00:17:30,254
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but since the engine is so good,
the suspension can't catch up.</b></font>

257
00:17:30,254 --> 00:17:33,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The engine is that good, huh?</b></font>

258
00:17:33,064 --> 00:17:35,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah, I love it.</b></font>

259
00:17:35,394 --> 00:17:38,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It sounds very tempting.</b></font>

260
00:17:38,734 --> 00:17:41,824
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I may want to ride with you next time.</b></font>

261
00:17:43,704 --> 00:17:47,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This car is very scary.</b></font>

262
00:17:47,704 --> 00:17:50,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's not for you to say, Bunta.</b></font>

263
00:17:50,874 --> 00:17:55,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I already know how scary your driving can be.</b></font>

264
00:17:55,584 --> 00:17:57,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Let me give you a glimpse.</b></font>

265
00:17:57,754 --> 00:17:59,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What?</b></font>

266
00:18:01,994 --> 00:18:04,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey, Bunta!</b></font>

267
00:18:04,194 --> 00:18:05,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>How did that happen?!</b></font>

268
00:18:05,694 --> 00:18:09,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You know, I needed to use this</b></font>

269
00:18:09,364 --> 00:18:11,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>as a wall to hold up my whole body.</b></font>

270
00:18:11,704 --> 00:18:15,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I used to think the side G-force in pass racing</b></font>

271
00:18:15,404 --> 00:18:18,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>wasn't worthy of a bucket seat.</b></font>

272
00:18:18,244 --> 00:18:24,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But I think my bones will bruise
if we don't put one in now.</b></font>

273
00:18:24,484 --> 00:18:27,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I've had enough for today.</b></font>

274
00:18:27,144 --> 00:18:29,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This is one tough customer.</b></font>

275
00:18:29,354 --> 00:18:32,254
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But that makes it more exciting.</b></font>

276
00:18:32,254 --> 00:18:36,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I still haven't decided
how I'm going to set it up.</b></font>

277
00:18:36,754 --> 00:18:40,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll take my time and enjoy it.</b></font>

278
00:18:40,264 --> 00:18:45,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I need to consider that inept Takumi
is going to be driving it, too.</b></font>

279
00:18:45,564 --> 00:18:47,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Inept, he says.</b></font>

280
00:18:47,064 --> 00:18:50,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takumi? Is he kidding?</b></font>

281
00:18:53,074 --> 00:18:56,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's kind of boring being in high school.</b></font>

282
00:18:56,744 --> 00:18:58,084
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You think so?</b></font>

283
00:18:58,084 --> 00:19:00,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I can't wait to start working.</b></font>

284
00:19:00,584 --> 00:19:05,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Until you have a real job, you're still a child.</b></font>

285
00:19:05,654 --> 00:19:09,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I wanna work and make money.</b></font>

286
00:19:09,024 --> 00:19:14,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>With a good job, I can have my own car.</b></font>

287
00:19:14,024 --> 00:19:18,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I can't buy anything now. How pathetic!</b></font>

288
00:19:18,034 --> 00:19:20,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Don't be so impatient.</b></font>

289
00:19:20,864 --> 00:19:24,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Whether we like it or not,
we're graduating next spring.</b></font>

290
00:19:24,544 --> 00:19:26,644
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I can't wait...</b></font>

291
00:19:26,644 --> 00:19:30,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...because there's nothing
worthwhile at school.</b></font>

292
00:19:30,474 --> 00:19:33,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You seem down, Takumi.</b></font>

293
00:19:52,834 --> 00:19:55,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Wait!</b></font>

294
00:19:55,034 --> 00:19:57,604
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Why have you been avoiding me?</b></font>

295
00:19:57,604 --> 00:20:00,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Did I do something wrong,</b></font>

296
00:20:00,404 --> 00:20:02,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>or say something hurtful?</b></font>

297
00:20:02,674 --> 00:20:06,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If so, please tell me. I'll apologize!</b></font>

298
00:20:06,884 --> 00:20:09,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Not really.</b></font>

299
00:20:09,454 --> 00:20:12,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Then what's wrong?
--Nothing's wrong.</b></font>

300
00:20:12,284 --> 00:20:14,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Something is clearly wrong!</b></font>

301
00:20:14,184 --> 00:20:17,254
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We were okay until recently.</b></font>

302
00:20:17,254 --> 00:20:20,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Now you seem distant. It's not fair.</b></font>

303
00:20:20,464 --> 00:20:22,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What's wrong, Takumi?</b></font>

304
00:20:22,764 --> 00:20:25,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't know why you're so worked up</b></font>

305
00:20:25,434 --> 00:20:27,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>about someone like me.</b></font>

306
00:20:27,804 --> 00:20:29,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It doesn't matter.</b></font>

307
00:20:29,974 --> 00:20:32,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's not like we're dating.</b></font>

308
00:20:32,804 --> 00:20:36,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That doesn't make any sense.
What's going on?</b></font>

